  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: August 4, 2025</em></p>

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy describes how GoalSteps ("we", "us", or "our") handles your information when you use our mobile application.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
  <p>
    GoalSteps does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data or sensitive user information. We do not require registration, login, or account creation of any kind.
  </p>

  <h2>2. No Advertising</h2>
  <p>
    Our app does not include any advertising services or third-party ad networks.
  </p>

  <h2>3. In-App Purchases & RevenueCat</h2>
  <p>
    We use <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">RevenueCat</a> as a third-party service to manage in-app subscriptions. RevenueCat does not access or store any personally identifiable information but may collect anonymous data such as purchase history to enable subscription functionality.
  </p>
  <p>
    For details on how RevenueCat handles data, please review their
    <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>
    Since we do not collect or store personal data, there is no risk of data leakage from our systems. Any data handled by third-party services is subject to their own security practices and privacy policies.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    GoalSteps does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13. The app is suitable for general audiences and does not contain age-restricted content.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:
    <br />
    <a href="mailto:newmonaalazz@gmail.com">newmonaalazz@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

